                      <locus target="#158v #175r" facs="159 175">158v, 175r, </locus> (full row of stops);
                      <locus target="#175r" facs="175">175r, </locus> (section divider using black and red);
                      <locus target="#1r #26r #91r #123v #130r #137r #151r" facs="001 026 091 124 130 137 151">1r, 26r, 91r, 123v, 130r, 137r, 151r</locus> (late <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐርገ፡</foreign> using crudely scribbled pencil or pen).
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                          <locus target="#175r" facs="175">Fol. 175r</locus>
                           <desc type="Asmat"><foreign xml:lang="gez">አስማት፡</foreign> prayer against the enemy, copied for <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወልደ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</foreign></desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc>Some psalms are marked with qǝb‘ that is serially numbered. It must have been used as a prayer on remedial oil.
                        Some versicles are encircled in ink. These were apparently the ones that are used in the liturgy.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                          <locus target="#ir(ecto)" facs="001">Fol. ir(ecto)</locus>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">The name <foreign xml:lang="gez">አብርሃ፡ ከሳይ፡</foreign>,
                           possible a one-time owner of the manuscript, and scribbling, in a crude hand</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">
                          <locus target="#72r #95r #104v #141r #143r #147v #148r #153r" facs="072 095 105 141 143 148 148 153">Fols. 72r, 95r, 104v, 141r, 143r, 147v, 148r, 153r</locus>)
                           <desc>Overlooked lines of text are added interlinearly</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                          <locus target="#29v" facs="030">Fol. 29v</locus>
                           <desc type="OwnershipNote">Note of ownership by <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቄስ፡ ሀደረ፡ አብርሃ፡</foreign></desc>
                           </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5">
                          <locus target="#40v" facs="041">Fol. 40v</locus>
                          <desc type="OwnershipNote"> Note of ownership by <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሀለቀ፡ ተስፋይ፡</foreign></desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6">
                          <locus target="#158v" facs="159">Fol. 158v</locus>
                          <desc type="OwnershipNote">The name of the original owner erased</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a7">
                          <locus target="#86r #158v" facs="086 159">Fols. 86r, 158v</locus>
